Package edu.rit.sha3

Package edu.rit.sha3 contains an implementation of the SHA-3 family of hash functions and the SHAKE family of extensible output hash functions for testing by the CryptoStat library.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SHA3_224
    Class SHA3_224 implements the SHA3-224 hash function with a 64-byte (512-bit) message.
    SHA3_256
    Class SHA3_256 implements the SHA3-256 hash function with a 64-byte (512-bit) message.
    SHA3_384
    Class SHA3_384 implements the SHA3-384 hash function with a 64-byte (512-bit) message.
    SHA3_512
    Class SHA3_512 implements the SHA3-512 hash function with a 64-byte (512-bit) message.
    SHA3Base
    Class SHA3Base is the abstract base class for the SHA-3 hash functions.
    SHAKE128
    Class SHAKE128 implements the SHAKE-128 extensible output hash function with a 64-byte (512-bit) message.
    SHAKE256
    Class SHAKE256 implements the SHAKE-256 extensible output hash function with a 64-byte (512-bit) message.

Package edu.rit.sha3 contains an implementation of the SHA-3 family of hash functions and the SHAKE family of extensible output hash functions for testing by the CryptoStat library.
